00:00:03.214 --> 00:00:07.095
namaskar
welcome to nishamadhulika.com

00:00:07.743 --> 00:00:11.068
we often make baingan sabzi which is really delicious.

00:00:11.486 --> 00:00:18.482
but baingan sabzi prepared with raddish leaves is more tasty.

00:00:18.874 --> 00:00:23.223
today we will make raddish leaves baingan sabzi.

00:00:23.537 --> 00:00:30.510
let's see what all ingredients are required for making raddish leaves baingan sabzi.

00:00:30.632 --> 00:00:33.934
brinjals - 2 (700 grams)

00:00:34.381 --> 00:00:40.056
raddish leaves - 1 bunch (remove stalk and wash thoroughly)

00:00:40.532 --> 00:00:42.952
tomato- 2 (finely chopped)

00:00:43.813 --> 00:00:45.829
turmeric powder - 1/2 tsp

00:00:46.022 --> 00:00:47.927
cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:48.270 --> 00:00:49.651
asafoetida - 2 pinch

00:00:49.946 --> 00:00:53.121
ginger - 1 inch piece (grated)

00:00:53.419 --> 00:00:55.927
green chilly - 2 (finely chopped)

00:00:56.302 --> 00:00:58.516
red chilly - 1/4 tsp

00:00:59.218 --> 00:01:01.266
coriander powder - 1 tsp

00:01:01.569 --> 00:01:04.578
salt - as per taste or 1 tsp

00:01:04.970 --> 00:01:07.922
garam masala - less then 1/4 tsp

00:01:08.378 --> 00:01:10.180
oil - 2 tbsp

00:01:10.515 --> 00:01:13.920
green coriande r- 1 tbsp (finely chopped)

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:17.091
finely chop the raddish leaves.

00:01:23.864 --> 00:01:28.419
wash and keep aside the leaves so that water dries up completely.

00:01:34.364 --> 00:01:43.393
you can cut leaves with choping board,knife or anything you feel is easy.

00:01:50.541 --> 00:01:52.121
now we will make sabzi.

00:01:52.151 --> 00:01:58.134
add oil in preheated pan.

00:02:02.805 --> 00:02:06.409
when oil gets hot add cumin seeds and asafoetida into it.

00:02:08.264 --> 00:02:19.321
after sauteing cumin seeds add turmeric powder,coriander powder and saute for while.

00:02:32.402 --> 00:02:36.751
stir the leaves nicely and add brinjals into it.

00:02:50.065 --> 00:02:55.073
we have already washed the brinjals now add them after cutting into pieces.

00:03:08.192 --> 00:03:18.883
add salt,red chilly powder,green chilly and ginger.

00:03:19.989 --> 00:03:26.309
mix and roast until all ingredients mix nicely.

00:03:33.239 --> 00:03:39.342
after mixing spices add 1 tbsp water in sabzi.

00:03:51.087 --> 00:03:55.151
cover and check for 5- 6 minutes and then check.

00:04:06.135 --> 00:04:12.857
sabzi is almost cooked but cover and cook for 2 more minutes.

00:04:37.949 --> 00:04:44.920
sabzi is cooked now add chopped tomatoes into it.

00:04:48.294 --> 00:04:53.548
increase the flame and cook until tomatoes get little tender.

00:04:55.586 --> 00:04:59.752
cover and cook for 2 minutes on low flame.

00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:06.395
you can also use mango powder instead of tomatoes to give it tart flavor.

00:05:08.172 --> 00:05:17.362
sabzi is ready,add garam masala and green coriander in the sabzi.

00:05:19.611 --> 00:05:23.659
eggplants with raddish leaves is ready.

00:05:24.584 --> 00:05:30.349
we haveused 700 grams brinjals and 1 bunch raddish leaves.

00:05:30.623 --> 00:05:35.171
this much quantity of sabzi can be served to 4-5 family members.

00:05:35.643 --> 00:05:42.448
serve this sabzi with chapatti,parantha or naan.

00:05:43.126 --> 00:05:49.574
try making this recipe and share your experiences with us.

00:05:49.777 --> 00:05:53.174
